RealTimeBattle is a programming game, in which robots controlled by the competitors programs are
fighting each other. Inspiration to the program came from
url(RobotBattle)(http://www.robotbattle.com/), a very interesting game, which however suffers from
two major drawbacks:

itemize(
   it() It is only available on an obscure windows manager called Windows.
   it() The robots are written in an own language, which restricts the possibilities to write
intelligent robots severely.
)


